{"title":"希望","authors":["束黎明","洪顺利"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":11,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"束黎明　摄影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪顺利　配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里离天空很近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又似乎离太阳很远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰山之父的威严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帕米尔高原的寒冷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还裹着小小的屋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕竟打开了小窗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨风吹进草的芬芳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缕缕晓光抚摸脸庞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心底有温泉在流淌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔吉克族的神鹰呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然还离不开襁褓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一首古老的歌谣在轻轻吟哦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支新生的鹰笛也在远处欢唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞上蓝天的希望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在母亲怀中孕育，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在孩子的梦中翱翔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交织成晃荡的绳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地摇，轻轻地荡……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}